4.title: The Internet Police for Mothers Day
4.plot: The Internet is full of material that people find offensive or something that they just don't like. A Tweet, Facebook post, News article even an Instagram photo can be found to offend your average citizen. In the digital age who will stand up for dignity and decency keeping the American citizen's feelings intact?? Look no further because the Internet Police Force are here. Take a walk with the latest in Internet policing as the officers take the law in a whole new direction. Watch what you post on the internet, They will find you and they will bust you.
